snippet.title: Skynet Rising Early Access Trailer #2
snippet.description:
Welcome to the world of Skynet Rising. From the mastermind creator Dr. Rex Havoc, Skynet Rising is a top notch action packed “Super Sandbox FPS”. Explore a beautifully crafted post apocalyptic world. Survive and conquer command towers through tough gun battles. Fight back to back with your brother in arms. Featuring a high adrenaline single player campaign, the game has a wickedly great Run and Gun gameplay with tons of "Shoot them in the face" fun. 

 Download here 🕹  http://bit.ly/2diTPVF
